  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function atomic_pointer_set(atomic: void, newval: void): void {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_atomic_pointer_set()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Sets the value of <code>atomic</code> to <code>newval</code>.</p>  <p>This call acts as a full compiler and hardware
memory barrier (after the set).</p>
  <p>Since 2.4</p>
